OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776442270
OL,3,CParents offered up to #150 per child
OL,4,Cunder Jersey Back-to-School Bonus
OL,6,FParents in Jersey will be able to
OL,7,Fapply for a Back-to-School Bonus of up
OL,8,Fto #150 per child from Reception to
OL,9,FYear 11.
OL,11,FThe Government says families with
OL,12,Fcombined earnings of up to #75,000
OL,13,Flast year will be eligible for the
OL,14,Fpayment, with #100 offered for each
OL,15,Fprimary school pupil and #150 for
OL,16,Fevery student in secondary education.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
