OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776442270
OL,3,CParents offered up to #150 per child
OL,4,Cunder Jersey Back-to-School Bonus
OL,6,FThey must be at school in Jersey in
OL,7,FSeptember and it is hoped the money
OL,8,Fcan be used to help offset cost-of-
OL,9,Fliving pressures when buying essential
OL,10,Fsupplies such as uniforms, shoes and
OL,11,Fstationery.
OL,13,FDetails of how to apply will be
OL,14,Freleased during the summer school
OL,15,Fterm, with the payment coming through
OL,16,Fas one lump sum per family in the
OL,17,Fsummer holidays.
OL,19,FThose on income support will receive
OL,20,Fthe money automatically.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776442270
OL,3,CParents offered up to #150 per child
OL,4,Cunder Jersey Back-to-School Bonus
OL,6,FJersey's Social Security Minister,
OL,7,FDeputy Lyndsay Feltham, says: "As part
OL,8,Fof the Government's commitment in the
OL,9,FBudget, I am pleased we are in a
OL,10,Fposition to introduce this Back-to-
OL,11,FSchool Bonus.
OL,13,F"I recognise the cost-of-living
OL,14,Fpressures many households are facing
OL,15,Fand it's important that we help where
OL,16,Fwe can to ease any financial stress on
OL,17,Ffamilies by ensuring children across
OL,18,Fthe island have the essentials they
OL,19,Fneed for the new school year."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
